    "Figure 5.8: Evaluation Graph of PPO (Reward During Algorithm's Run) RQ2 ConclusionThe results demonstrate that while the choice of RL algorithms may not lead to significant differences in WCET estimation, incorporating diversity into the reward functions has a substantial impact.",
    "In all cases, agents using the diversity reward outperform those without it, regardless of the RL algorithm applied.",
    "This suggests that incorporating diversity enables the exploration of a broader range of solutions, preventing premature convergence to suboptimal solutions.",
